{
  "_comment": "accelya-pipeline-<learner> CloudWatch dashboard. Four-row grid answering Flowing / Correct / Fast / Cheap. Trainer deploy script substitutes <learner> + <account> and strips _comment keys before put-dashboard.",
  "widgets": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 24, "height": 1,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "## Accelya Pipeline · <learner>\n**Row 1: Flowing?** · **Row 2: Correct?** · **Row 3: Fast?** · **Row 4: Cheap?**",
        "background": "transparent"
      }
    },

    {
      "_section": "ROW 1 — FLOWING?",
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0, "y": 1, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Kinesis IncomingRecords (cancellation-events-<learner>)",
        "metrics": [
          ["AWS/Kinesis", "IncomingRecords", "StreamName", "cancellation-events-<learner>", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "records / 1-min"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 60,
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false,
        "yAxis": {"left": {"min": 0}}
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 8, "y": 1, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "SQS Depth (review queue + DLQ)",
        "metrics": [
          ["AWS/SQS", "ApproximateNumberOfMessagesVisible", "QueueName", "model-review-queue-<learner>", {"stat": "Maximum", "label": "review queue"}],
          ["AWS/SQS", "ApproximateNumberOfMessagesVisible", "QueueName", "stream-dlq-<learner>", {"stat": "Maximum", "label": "DLQ"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 60,
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 16, "y": 1, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "SFN Executions (inference-pipeline-<learner>)",
        "metrics": [
          ["AWS/States", "ExecutionsStarted", "StateMachineArn", "arn:aws:states:ap-south-1:<account>:stateMachine:inference-pipeline-<learner>", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "started", "id": "m1"}],
          ["AWS/States", "ExecutionsSucceeded", "StateMachineArn", "arn:aws:states:ap-south-1:<account>:stateMachine:inference-pipeline-<learner>", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "succeeded", "id": "m2"}],
          ["AWS/States", "ExecutionsFailed", "StateMachineArn", "arn:aws:states:ap-south-1:<account>:stateMachine:inference-pipeline-<learner>", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "failed", "id": "m3", "color": "#d62728"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 60,
        "view": "timeSeries"
      }
    },

    {
      "_section": "ROW 2 — CORRECT?",
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0, "y": 6, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Confidence routing (predict)",
        "metrics": [
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "RecordsOk", "service", "predict-cancel-risk", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "ok records"}],
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "LowConfidenceCount", "service", "predict-cancel-risk", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "low-conf routed to review", "color": "#d62728"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 300,
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 8, "y": 6, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "SFN failures + timeouts",
        "metrics": [
          ["AWS/States", "ExecutionsFailed", "StateMachineArn", "arn:aws:states:ap-south-1:<account>:stateMachine:inference-pipeline-<learner>", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "failed"}],
          ["AWS/States", "ExecutionsTimedOut", "StateMachineArn", "arn:aws:states:ap-south-1:<account>:stateMachine:inference-pipeline-<learner>", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "timed out"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 300,
        "view": "timeSeries"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 16, "y": 6, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "RecordsErr per Lambda (Sum, 5 min)",
        "metrics": [
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "RecordsErr", "service", "validator", {"stat": "Sum"}],
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "RecordsErr", "service", "consumer", {"stat": "Sum"}],
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "RecordsErr", "service", "bedrock-enrich", {"stat": "Sum"}],
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "RecordsErr", "service", "predict-cancel-risk", {"stat": "Sum"}],
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "RecordsErr", "service", "persist-enriched", {"stat": "Sum"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 300,
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false
      }
    },

    {
      "_section": "ROW 3 — FAST?",
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0, "y": 11, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Lambda Duration p99 (5 hot ones)",
        "metrics": [
          ["AWS/Lambda", "Duration", "FunctionName", "accelya-validator-trainer", {"stat": "p99"}],
          ["AWS/Lambda", "Duration", "FunctionName", "accelya-consumer-trainer", {"stat": "p99"}],
          ["AWS/Lambda", "Duration", "FunctionName", "accelya-bedrock-enrich-trainer", {"stat": "p99"}],
          ["AWS/Lambda", "Duration", "FunctionName", "accelya-predict-cancel-risk-trainer", {"stat": "p99"}],
          ["AWS/Lambda", "Duration", "FunctionName", "accelya-persist-enriched-trainer", {"stat": "p99"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 60,
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 8, "y": 11, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Bedrock InvocationLatency p99 + Throttles",
        "metrics": [
          ["AWS/Bedrock", "InvocationLatency", "ModelId", "apac.anthropic.claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022-v2:0", {"stat": "p99", "label": "p99 ms"}],
          ["AWS/Bedrock", "InvocationThrottles", "ModelId", "apac.anthropic.claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022-v2:0", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "throttles", "yAxis": "right", "color": "#d62728"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 60,
        "view": "timeSeries"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 16, "y": 11, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "SageMaker ModelLatency + ModelSetupTime",
        "metrics": [
          ["AWS/SageMaker", "ModelLatency", "EndpointName", "accelya-cancel-risk-<learner>", "VariantName", "AllTraffic", {"stat": "p99", "label": "p99 ms"}],
          ["AWS/SageMaker", "ModelSetupTime", "EndpointName", "accelya-cancel-risk-<learner>", "VariantName", "AllTraffic", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "cold-start ms (sum)", "color": "#d62728"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 60,
        "view": "timeSeries"
      }
    },

    {
      "_section": "ROW 4 — CHEAP?",
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0, "y": 16, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Bedrock tokens (input + output, Sum/5min)",
        "metrics": [
          ["AWS/Bedrock", "InputTokenCount", "ModelId", "apac.anthropic.claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022-v2:0", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "input"}],
          ["AWS/Bedrock", "OutputTokenCount", "ModelId", "apac.anthropic.claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022-v2:0", {"stat": "Sum", "label": "output"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 300,
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 8, "y": 16, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Bedrock $/hour (extrapolated from 5-min sums)",
        "metrics": [
          [{"expression": "(m1 + m2) * 0.003 / 1000 * 12", "label": "$/hour", "id": "e1"}],
          ["AWS/Bedrock", "InputTokenCount", "ModelId", "apac.anthropic.claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022-v2:0", {"id": "m1", "stat": "Sum", "visible": false}],
          ["AWS/Bedrock", "OutputTokenCount", "ModelId", "apac.anthropic.claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022-v2:0", {"id": "m2", "stat": "Sum", "visible": false}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 300,
        "view": "timeSeries"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 16, "y": 16, "width": 8, "height": 5,
      "properties": {
        "title": "CostPerRecordEstimate (EMF, avg)",
        "metrics": [
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "CostPerRecordEstimate", "service", "bedrock-enrich", {"stat": "Average", "label": "bedrock $/record"}],
          ["Accelya/Pipeline", "CostPerRecordEstimate", "service", "predict-cancel-risk", {"stat": "Average", "label": "predict $/record"}]
        ],
        "region": "ap-south-1",
        "period": 300,
        "view": "timeSeries"
      }
    },

    {
      "_section": "FOOTER",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0, "y": 21, "width": 24, "height": 2,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "**Alarms:** iterator-age · bedrock-throttle · confidence-drift → SNS `accelya-alarms-<learner>` · Cost Anomaly Detection (us-east-1) → same SNS topic.\n**X-Ray:** TracingConfig Active on all 10 Lambdas + SFN; traceHeader propagated by consumer. View service map → CloudWatch → X-Ray traces.",
        "background": "transparent"
      }
    }
  ]
}
